ews/wanderers-get-valuable-point-against-city\n| team2      = [[Western Sydney Wanderers FC|Western Sydney Wanderers]]\n| goals1     = \n* [[Jamie Maclaren|Maclaren]] {{goal|30|pen.}}\n| goals2     = \n* [[Tate Russell|Russell]] {{goal|21}}\n| location   = [[Melbourne]]\n| stadium    = [[Melbourne Rectangular Stadium|AAMI Park]]\n| attendance = 2,292\n| referee    = [[Kate Jacewicz]]\n| result     = D\n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n| round      = 24\n| date       = 21 March 2020\n| time       = 19:30 [[UTC+11:00|AEDT]]\n| team1      = [[Western Sydney Wanderers FC|Western Sydney Wanderers]]\n| score      = 1\u20131 \n| report     = https://www.a-league.com.au/match/id/2024062\n| team2      = [[Sydney FC]]\n| goals1     =\n* [[Kwame Yeboah|Yeboah]] {{goal|82}} \n| goals2     =\n* [[Adam le Fondre|le Fondre]] {{goal|35}} \n| location   = [[Sydney]]\n| stadium    = [[Western Sydney Stadium|Bankwest Stadium]]\n| attendance = 0 \n| referee    =Shaun Evans \n| result     = D \n}}\n{{football box collapsible\n| round      = 25\n| date       = TBD\n| time       = TBD\n| team1      = [[Western United FC|Western United]]\n| score      = Postponed\n| report     = [https://www.wswanderersfc.com.au/news/hyundai-a-league-201920-postponed Postponement]\n| team2      = [[Western Sydney Wanderers FC|Western Sydney Wanderers]]\n| goals1     = \n| goals2     = \n| location   = [[Ballarat]]\n| stadium    = [[Eureka Stadium|Mars Stadium]]\n| attendance = \n| referee    = \n| result     = V\n}}\n{{football box collapsible \n| round      = 26\n| date       = TBD\n| time       = TBD\n| team1      = [[Western Sydney Wanderers FC|Western Sydney Wanderers]]\n| score      = Postponed\n| report     = [https://www.wswanderersfc.com.au/news/hyundai-a-league-201920-postponed Postponement]\n| team2      = [[Perth Glory FC|Perth Glory]]\n| goals1     =\n| goals2     = \n| location   = [[Sydney]]\n| stadium    = [[Western Sydney Stadium|Bankwest Stadium]]\n| attendance =  \n| referee    = \n| resul