{"title_page": "Wemeldinge", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                            = Wemeldinge\n| image_skyline                   = Wemeldinge.jpg\n| image_caption                   = De kerk van Wemeldinge <br> (Church of Wemeldinge)\n| image_flag                      = Flag of Wemeldinge.svg\n| image_shield                    = Wemeldinge wapen.svg\n| coordinates                     = {{coord|51|31|3|N|3|59|44|E|region:NL|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type                = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n| subdivision_name                = [[Netherlands]]\n| subdivision_type1               = Province\n| subdivision_name1               = [[Zeeland]]\n| subdivision_type2               = Municipality\n| subdivision_name2               = [[Kapelle]]\n| area_total_km2                  = \n| population                      = 3091\n| population_as_of                = 1 January 2009\n| website                         = \n| official_name                   = \n| native_name                     = {{native name|nl|Weumeldienge}}\n}}\n\n'''Wemeldinge''' is the oldest village in the [[Zuid-Beveland]] area of the [[Netherlands|Dutch]] province of [[Zeeland]]. It is located in the municipality of [[Kapelle]], about 4&nbsp;km northwest of [[Yerseke]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mkbwemeldinge.nl/|title=Home - Wemeldinge.info|last=jswebdesign-webmaster|website=mkbwemeldinge.nl|language=nl-nl|access-date=2020-04-06}}</ref>. It is located within the [[Eastern Scheldt]] [[List of national parks of the Netherlands|national park]].\n\nWemeldinge was a separate municipality until 1970, when it was merged with [[Kapelle]].<ref>{{Repertorium Nederlandse Gemeenten}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Kuyper|Wemeldinge|ze|wemeldingen}} Map of the former municipality, around 1868.\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Zeeland]]\n[[Category:Former municipalities of Zeeland]]\n[[Category:Kapelle]]\n\n\n{{Zeeland-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                = WEUMELINGE\n| image_skyline       = Wemeldinge.jpg\n| image_caption       = De kerk van Wemeldinge <br> (Church of Wemeldinge)\n| image_flag          = Flag of Wemeldinge.svg\n| image_shield        = Wemeldinge wapen.svg\n| coordinates         = {{coord|51|31|3|N|3|59|44|E|region:NL|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type    = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n| subdivision_name    = [[Netherlands]]\n| subdivision_type1   = Province\n| subdivision_name1   = [[Zeeland]]\n| subdivision_type2   = Municipality\n| subdivision_name2   = [[Kapelle]]\n| area_total_km2      = \n| population          = 3091\n| population_as_of    = 1 January 2009\n| website             = \n}}\n\n'''Wemeldinge''' is a village in the [[Netherlands|Dutch]] province of [[Zeeland]]. It is located in the municipality of [[Kapelle]], about 4&nbsp;km northwest of [[Yerseke]].\n\nWemeldinge was a separate municipality until 1970, when it was merged with [[Kapelle]].<ref>{{Repertorium Nederlandse Gemeenten}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Kuyper|Wemeldinge|ze|wemeldingen}} Map of the former municipality, around 1868.\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Zeeland]]\n[[Category:Former municipalities of Zeeland]]\n[[Category:Kapelle]]\n\n\n{{Zeeland-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Lord of the East", "label": "safe", "comment": "Added minor source additions. Added native language to infobox.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wemeldinge"}
